h: Move left by one character.
Usage: Navigate left in Normal mode.

j: Move down by one line.
Usage: Navigate downwards in Normal mode.

k: Move up by one line.
Usage: Navigate upwards in Normal mode.

l: Move right by one character.
Usage: Navigate right in Normal mode.

0: Move to the beginning of the line.
Usage: Position the cursor at the start of the current line.

$: Move to the end of the line.
Usage: Position the cursor at the end of the current line.

gg: Move to the beginning of the file.
Usage: Jump to the first line of the file.

G: Move to the end of the file.
Usage: Jump to the last line of the file.

Ctrl + f: Page forward.
Usage: Scroll down one page.

Ctrl + b: Page backward.
Usage: Scroll up one page.

w: Move forward by a word.
Usage: Move the cursor to the start of the next word.

b: Move backward by a word.
Usage: Move the cursor to the beginning of the previous word.

